{"tid":2187923,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"某晚我去了某快餐店食二手飯（真實版）","createTime":"2020-09-04T02:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T02:49:23.000Z","uid":261388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4b92afbc3a92af696db3e6539ba9d7a03ffbb0c0","tid":2187923,"uid":261388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T02:40:05.000Z","msg":"我永遠唔會忘記昨晚..<br />\n<br />\n我已經四日沒有東西落肚，昨晚終於忍不住，真的很肚餓，餓到連尊嚴也不顧...<br />\n沒有辦法，身上已無分文，屋企人又唔理，又找不到工作，連八達通的五十蚊按金也拿走了..<br />\n<br />\n吃二手飯的感覺真的很難堪，昨晚在某屋村的快餐店，吃了別人剩下的飯餸，理不了別人的目光，一邊食眼淚俏俏的在眼角滴下......我是一塊窮西 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FZxO1nE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFZxO1nE.png&h=b796344c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4d77d57b9d2707a19aa57a53acf91a4b6b9b485","tid":2187923,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T02:49:23.000Z","msg":"求下大家唔好放棄12位送中手足！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2187893\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2187893</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}